*Yuanshou (元狩) 122 BC – 117 BC
*Yuanding (元鼎) 116 BC – 111 BC
*Yuanfeng (元封) 110 BC – 105 BC
*Taichu (太初) 104 BC – 101 BC
*Tianhan (天漢) 100 BC – 97 BC
*Taishi (太始) 96 BC – 93 BC
*Zhenghe (征和) 92 BC – 89 BC
*Houyuan (後元) 88 BC – 87 BC

